data.description: Your next home is here! This adorable split-entry home in the highly desired Keystone area has plenty of updates. Plus it's near all the amenities the Keystone area has to offer! Tall and vaulted ceilings on the main level with tons of natural light through large windows. Informal dining area leads to brand new deck just steps from the kitchen. Three bedrooms on the main living level along with a finished walk-out lower level! Fully fenced backyard and beautiful landscaping. Great views from the deck to the south. You're going to want to see this!
